Pokémon Information Viewer
Description:
This project uses the Pokémon API to fetch and display various information about Pokémon, their types, and abilities.

Features:

Get detailed information about a specific Pokémon.
List all Pokémon types.
Fetch information about a specific Pokémon type.
List all Pokémon abilities.
Fetch information about a specific Pokémon ability.

Setup Instructions:

1. Install the required packages in bash:
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run the project:
python currency_exchange.py
